{"video_id": "mtCACpI1Yt4", "title": "SB 1.18.4-5 | HH Stoka Krishna Swami | 27-03-2023 | Daily Evening Bhagavatam Discourse", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mtCACpI1Yt4", "duration": 905, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 4.9, "text": " Om Agyanati Miran Dhasya Gyananj Nishalakaya"}, {"start": 4.9, "end": 9.5, "text": " Chakshurun Militam Yena Tasmai Shri Gurave Namaha"}, {"start": 9.5, "end": 13.82, "text": " Namah Om Vishnupadaya Krishna Preshtaya Bhutale"}, {"start": 13.82, "end": 17.96, "text": " Srimate Bhaktivedanta Swamin Nithinamine"}, {"start": 17.96, "end": 22.84, "text": " Namaste Saraswate Deve Gauravani Pracharine"}, {"start": 22.84, "end": 27.46, "text": " Nirvishesha Shunyavadi Pashchatyade Shatarine"}, {"start": 27.46, "end": 31.98, "text": " Jaya Shri Krishna Chaitanya Prabhu Nithyananda"}, {"start": 31.98, "end": 37.32, "text": " Shri Advaita Gadadhara Shri Vasadi Gaurabhakta Vrinda"}, {"start": 37.32, "end": 42.32, "text": " Hare Krishna Hare Krishna Krishna Krishna Hare Hare"}, {"start": 42.32, "end": 46.86, "text": " Hare Rama Hare Rama Rama Rama Hare Hare"}, {"start": 46.86, "end": 50.78, "text": " Om Namo Bhagavate Vasudevaya"}, {"start": 50.78, "end": 55.24, "text": " Narayanam Namaskritya Naramchaiva Narottamam"}, {"start": 55.24, "end": 57.24, "text": " Devim Saraswati Narottamam"}, {"start": 57.46, "end": 61.46, "text": " Vyasam Tatho Jayam Udi Rayet"}, {"start": 61.46, "end": 69.46000000000001, "text": " In this session we will be discussing from the first canto, 18th chapter of the Srimad Bhagavatam, verse numbers 4 and 5."}, {"start": 69.46000000000001, "end": 73.46000000000001, "text": " The fourth verse we will discuss first."}, {"start": 73.46000000000001, "end": 77.46000000000001, "text": " Nottama Shloka Vartanam"}, {"start": 77.46000000000001, "end": 80.46000000000001, "text": " Jushatam Tath Kathamritam"}, {"start": 80.46000000000001, "end": 84.46000000000001, "text": " Syat Sambhramo Antakalepi"}, {"start": 84.46000000000001, "end": 87.46000000000001, "text": " Smaratam Tath Padambhujam"}, {"start": 87.46000000000001, "end": 90.46000000000001, "text": " The meaning of this verse is"}, {"start": 90.46000000000001, "end": 99.46000000000001, "text": " This was so because those who have dedicated their lives to the transcendental topics of the personality of Godhead"}, {"start": 99.46000000000001, "end": 102.46000000000001, "text": " of whom the Vedic hymns sing"}, {"start": 102.46000000000001, "end": 108.46000000000001, "text": " and who are constantly engaged in remembering the lotus feet of the Lord"}, {"start": 108.46000000000001, "end": 116.46000000000001, "text": " do not run the risk of having misconceptions even at the last moment of their lives."}, {"start": 117.46000000000001, "end": 127.46000000000001, "text": " So, this verse has got a reference to the previous verse"}, {"start": 127.46000000000001, "end": 130.46, "text": " because the verse says"}, {"start": 130.46, "end": 132.46, "text": " This was so because"}, {"start": 132.46, "end": 134.46, "text": " What was so?"}, {"start": 134.46, "end": 138.46, "text": " That Parikshit Maharaj"}, {"start": 138.46, "end": 145.46, "text": " surrendered himself unto Shri Lashukadeva Goswami"}, {"start": 145.46, "end": 146.46, "text": " and therefore"}, {"start": 146.46, "end": 152.46, "text": " he was able to understand the actual position of the personality of Godhead."}, {"start": 152.46, "end": 157.46, "text": " So, the fourth verse that today we are discussing now"}, {"start": 157.46, "end": 162.46, "text": " has got relevance"}, {"start": 162.46, "end": 167.46, "text": " to this point made in the third verse"}, {"start": 167.46, "end": 174.46, "text": " that he was able to understand the actual position of the personality of Godhead because"}, {"start": 174.46, "end": 185.46, "text": " the nature of a person"}, {"start": 185.46, "end": 190.46, "text": " who has dedicated his life"}, {"start": 190.46, "end": 194.46, "text": " to the transcendental topics of the personality of Godhead"}, {"start": 194.46, "end": 200.46, "text": " and such people also"}, {"start": 200.46, "end": 202.46, "text": " are constantly engaged in remembering the lotus feet of the Lord."}, {"start": 202.46, "end": 209.46, "text": " Two characteristics."}, {"start": 209.46, "end": 211.46, "text": " First one is"}, {"start": 211.46, "end": 213.46, "text": " their lives are dedicated"}, {"start": 213.46, "end": 218.46, "text": " to the transcendental topics of the personality of Godhead."}, {"start": 218.46, "end": 221.46, "text": " They live their life based on"}, {"start": 221.46, "end": 227.46, "text": " the scriptures which glorify the Supreme Lord and His pure devotees."}, {"start": 227.46, "end": 228.46, "text": " And"}, {"start": 228.46, "end": 230.46, "text": " they also"}, {"start": 230.46, "end": 232.46, "text": " constantly"}, {"start": 232.46, "end": 235.46, "text": " think of the lotus feet of the Lord,"}, {"start": 235.46, "end": 237.46, "text": " Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 237.46, "end": 239.46, "text": " Such"}, {"start": 239.46, "end": 241.46, "text": " devotees"}, {"start": 241.46, "end": 243.46, "text": " they do not"}, {"start": 243.46, "end": 245.46, "text": " have the"}, {"start": 245.46, "end": 247.46, "text": " risk"}, {"start": 247.46, "end": 249.46, "text": " of having misconceptions"}, {"start": 249.46, "end": 251.46, "text": " at the"}, {"start": 251.46, "end": 253.46, "text": " end of their lives."}, {"start": 253.46, "end": 257.46000000000004, "text": " So, Srila Prabhupada explains what is this risk"}, {"start": 257.46000000000004, "end": 260.46000000000004, "text": " that somebody may have."}, {"start": 260.46000000000004, "end": 261.46000000000004, "text": " Hmm."}, {"start": 261.46, "end": 263.46, "text": " So, in the purport,"}, {"start": 263.46, "end": 266.46, "text": " Srila Prabhupada explains,"}, {"start": 266.46, "end": 270.46, "text": " the highest perfection of life is attained"}, {"start": 270.46, "end": 273.46, "text": " by remembering the transcendental nature"}, {"start": 273.46, "end": 274.46, "text": " of the Lord"}, {"start": 274.46, "end": 281.46, "text": " at the last moment of one's life."}, {"start": 281.46, "end": 284.46, "text": " We are spiritual beings."}, {"start": 284.46, "end": 288.46, "text": " The Supreme Lord is completely a spiritual personality."}, {"start": 288.46, "end": 290.46, "text": " We belong"}, {"start": 290.46, "end": 296.46, "text": " to the Supreme Lord's personal abode."}, {"start": 296.46, "end": 297.46, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 297.46, "end": 300.46, "text": " in this human form of life,"}, {"start": 300.46, "end": 305.46, "text": " we are meant to cultivate Krishna Consciousness"}, {"start": 305.46, "end": 311.46, "text": " to be able to remember the Supreme Lord at the end of our life."}, {"start": 311.46, "end": 314.46, "text": " Ante Narayanas Pratihi."}, {"start": 314.46, "end": 319.46, "text": " Antakale Chamameva Svaranmuktva Kalevaram."}, {"start": 319.46, "end": 323.46, "text": " Both the Bhagavatam and the Bhagavad Gita describe this."}, {"start": 323.46, "end": 324.46, "text": " Hmm."}, {"start": 324.46, "end": 326.46, "text": " At the end of life,"}, {"start": 326.46, "end": 329.46, "text": " to successfully terminate this"}, {"start": 329.46, "end": 331.46, "text": " ah"}, {"start": 331.46, "end": 332.46, "text": " life,"}, {"start": 332.46, "end": 336.46, "text": " one has to remember Krishna at the last moment."}, {"start": 336.46, "end": 338.46, "text": " Hmm."}, {"start": 338.46, "end": 341.46, "text": " And that is the highest perfection because"}, {"start": 341.46, "end": 344.46, "text": " simply by remembering Krishna alone"}, {"start": 344.46, "end": 346.46, "text": " at the end of one's life,"}, {"start": 346.46, "end": 349.46, "text": " one is able to attain"}, {"start": 349.46, "end": 352.46, "text": " immediately"}, {"start": 352.46, "end": 355.46, "text": " the transcendental abode of the Supreme Lord,"}, {"start": 355.46, "end": 360.46, "text": " never to take birth again in this miserable material world."}, {"start": 360.46, "end": 362.46, "text": " And having gone there,"}, {"start": 362.46, "end": 364.46, "text": " what do they do?"}, {"start": 364.46, "end": 367.46, "text": " They live eternal life full of bliss and knowledge"}, {"start": 367.46, "end": 370.46, "text": " in the association of the Supreme Personality of Godhead,"}, {"start": 370.46, "end": 375.46, "text": " being engaged in His loving devotional service"}, {"start": 375.46, "end": 378.46, "text": " very naturally."}, {"start": 379.46, "end": 382.46, "text": " So Srila Prabhupada further explains,"}, {"start": 382.46, "end": 385.46, "text": " this perfection of life is made possible"}, {"start": 385.46, "end": 388.46, "text": " by one who has learned the actual transcendental nature"}, {"start": 388.46, "end": 391.46, "text": " of the Lord from the Vedic hymns"}, {"start": 391.46, "end": 394.46, "text": " sung by a liberated soul like Shukadev Goswami"}, {"start": 394.46, "end": 400.46, "text": " or someone in that line of disciplic succession."}, {"start": 400.46, "end": 403.46, "text": " So how do you actually ensure"}, {"start": 403.46, "end": 408.46, "text": " that you'll be able to remember the Supreme Lord at the end of your life?"}, {"start": 408.46000000000004, "end": 410.46000000000004, "text": " So for that,"}, {"start": 410.46000000000004, "end": 413.46000000000004, "text": " you have to learn"}, {"start": 413.46000000000004, "end": 416.46000000000004, "text": " what is this transcendental nature"}, {"start": 416.46000000000004, "end": 419.46000000000004, "text": " of the Supreme Lord Krishna"}, {"start": 419.46000000000004, "end": 421.46000000000004, "text": " by hearing from"}, {"start": 421.46000000000004, "end": 426.46000000000004, "text": " a liberated soul like Shukadev Goswami"}, {"start": 426.46000000000004, "end": 428.46000000000004, "text": " or someone"}, {"start": 428.46000000000004, "end": 430.46000000000004, "text": " in the"}, {"start": 430.46000000000004, "end": 435.46000000000004, "text": " parampara from Shukadev Goswami"}, {"start": 435.46000000000004, "end": 437.46000000000004, "text": " who is also a liberated soul."}, {"start": 438.46000000000004, "end": 441.46000000000004, "text": " Now,"}, {"start": 441.46000000000004, "end": 444.46000000000004, "text": " if somebody simply hears"}, {"start": 444.46000000000004, "end": 446.46000000000004, "text": " this type of Krishna Katha,"}, {"start": 446.46000000000004, "end": 448.46000000000004, "text": " Bhagavad Katha"}, {"start": 448.46000000000004, "end": 451.46000000000004, "text": " from some mental speculator,"}, {"start": 451.46000000000004, "end": 455.46000000000004, "text": " Srila Prabhupada says there's no use."}, {"start": 455.46000000000004, "end": 457.46000000000004, "text": " You have to hear"}, {"start": 457.46000000000004, "end": 462.46000000000004, "text": " from an actual self-realized soul"}, {"start": 462.46000000000004, "end": 464.46000000000004, "text": " and"}, {"start": 464.46000000000004, "end": 467.46000000000004, "text": " the hearing process is also"}, {"start": 467.46000000000004, "end": 470.46000000000004, "text": " directed"}, {"start": 470.46000000000004, "end": 473.46000000000004, "text": " that one has to properly understand"}, {"start": 473.46000000000004, "end": 476.46000000000004, "text": " the transcendental nature of Krishna"}, {"start": 476.46000000000004, "end": 480.46000000000004, "text": " by service and submission."}, {"start": 480.46000000000004, "end": 483.46000000000004, "text": " One should be surrendered to the spiritual master"}, {"start": 483.46000000000004, "end": 486.46000000000004, "text": " and one should render service to the spiritual master."}, {"start": 486.46000000000004, "end": 490.46000000000004, "text": " Then the spiritual master reveals"}, {"start": 490.46000000000004, "end": 491.46000000000004, "text": " the secret,"}, {"start": 491.46000000000004, "end": 492.46000000000004, "text": " the truth,"}, {"start": 492.46000000000004, "end": 496.46000000000004, "text": " the most confidential knowledge about the"}, {"start": 496.46000000000004, "end": 499.46000000000004, "text": " transcendental nature of"}, {"start": 499.46000000000004, "end": 503.46000000000004, "text": " the Supreme Personality of God, Krishna."}, {"start": 503.46000000000004, "end": 505.46000000000004, "text": " And everything becomes"}, {"start": 505.46000000000004, "end": 508.46000000000004, "text": " transparently clear,"}, {"start": 508.46000000000004, "end": 511.46000000000004, "text": " very, very clear."}, {"start": 511.46000000000004, "end": 513.46, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 513.46, "end": 516.46, "text": " by such clear understanding,"}, {"start": 516.46, "end": 520.46, "text": " by realization,"}, {"start": 520.46, "end": 522.46, "text": " one is able to"}, {"start": 522.46, "end": 525.46, "text": " live transcendentally"}, {"start": 525.46, "end": 528.46, "text": " even before death comes."}, {"start": 528.46, "end": 530.46, "text": " One's life is"}, {"start": 530.46, "end": 532.46, "text": " life dedicated to"}, {"start": 532.46, "end": 534.46, "text": " the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 534.46, "end": 537.46, "text": " And such a"}, {"start": 537.46, "end": 540.46, "text": " transcendental living continues"}, {"start": 540.46, "end": 542.46, "text": " till the end of life."}, {"start": 542.46, "end": 544.46, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 544.46, "end": 546.46, "text": " Srila Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 546.46, "end": 548.46, "text": " by scientific adaptation,"}, {"start": 548.46, "end": 550.46, "text": " one is able to remember the Lord"}, {"start": 550.46, "end": 552.46, "text": " even at the time of death."}, {"start": 552.46, "end": 554.46, "text": " What happens at the time of death?"}, {"start": 554.46, "end": 556.46, "text": " Why is it"}, {"start": 556.46, "end": 558.46, "text": " difficult to remember normally"}, {"start": 558.46, "end": 560.46, "text": " for an ordinary person?"}, {"start": 560.46, "end": 561.46, "text": " That is because"}, {"start": 561.46, "end": 564.46, "text": " at the time of death,"}, {"start": 564.46, "end": 567.46, "text": " the power of remembrance is slackened"}, {"start": 567.46, "end": 571.46, "text": " due to derangement of bodily membranes."}, {"start": 571.46, "end": 573.46, "text": " Something happens in this body"}, {"start": 573.46, "end": 574.46, "text": " when"}, {"start": 574.46, "end": 576.46, "text": " the time of death comes."}, {"start": 576.46, "end": 578.46, "text": " We have to leave the body."}, {"start": 578.46, "end": 580.46, "text": " The bodily functions"}, {"start": 580.46, "end": 583.46, "text": " are going to completely stop working."}, {"start": 583.46, "end": 585.46, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 585.46, "end": 587.46, "text": " at that moment,"}, {"start": 587.46, "end": 589.46, "text": " last moment,"}, {"start": 589.46, "end": 591.46, "text": " it's not easy,"}, {"start": 591.46, "end": 593.46, "text": " it's not natural"}, {"start": 593.46, "end": 597.46, "text": " to remember the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 597.46, "end": 600.46, "text": " For a common man,"}, {"start": 600.46, "end": 602.46, "text": " it is very difficult to remember things"}, {"start": 602.46, "end": 605.46, "text": " as they are at the time of death."}, {"start": 605.46, "end": 607.46, "text": " But by the grace of the Lord"}, {"start": 607.46, "end": 609.46, "text": " and His bona fide devotees,"}, {"start": 609.46, "end": 611.46, "text": " the spiritual masters,"}, {"start": 611.46, "end": 612.46, "text": " one can get this opportunity"}, {"start": 612.46, "end": 614.46, "text": " without difficulty."}, {"start": 614.46, "end": 616.46, "text": " So, what really works?"}, {"start": 616.46, "end": 619.46, "text": " Actually, it is the grace of the Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 619.46, "end": 621.46, "text": " and His pure devotees,"}, {"start": 621.46, "end": 623.46, "text": " the spiritual masters."}, {"start": 623.46, "end": 627.46, "text": " That is the real secret."}, {"start": 627.46, "end": 630.46, "text": " And who can have that"}, {"start": 630.46, "end": 633.46, "text": " mercy or grace?"}, {"start": 633.46, "end": 635.46, "text": " Those who have dedicated their life"}, {"start": 635.46, "end": 637.46, "text": " for serving the Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 637.46, "end": 639.46, "text": " under the guidance of"}, {"start": 639.46, "end": 641.46, "text": " the bona fide spiritual master."}, {"start": 642.46, "end": 643.46, "text": " And that was the case"}, {"start": 643.46, "end": 645.46, "text": " with Maharaj Pariksit."}, {"start": 645.46, "end": 647.46, "text": " His life was dedicated"}, {"start": 647.46, "end": 649.46, "text": " for Krishna's service."}, {"start": 649.46, "end": 651.46, "text": " And he got a"}, {"start": 651.46, "end": 653.46, "text": " very, very"}, {"start": 657.46, "end": 659.46, "text": " able spiritual master"}, {"start": 659.46, "end": 661.46, "text": " like Shukadeva Goswami."}, {"start": 661.46, "end": 663.46, "text": " The fifth verse,"}, {"start": 663.46, "end": 665.46, "text": " Tavit kalina prabhavet"}, {"start": 665.46, "end": 668.46, "text": " pravishto piha sarvatah"}, {"start": 668.46, "end": 670.46, "text": " yavad isho mahan urvyam"}, {"start": 670.46, "end": 673.46, "text": " abhimanyava ekarat"}, {"start": 673.46, "end": 675.46, "text": " The meaning of this fifth verse is,"}, {"start": 675.46, "end": 677.46, "text": " as long as the great powerful"}, {"start": 677.46, "end": 679.46, "text": " son of Abhimanyu remains"}, {"start": 679.46, "end": 681.46, "text": " the emperor of the world,"}, {"start": 681.46, "end": 682.46, "text": " there is no chance"}, {"start": 682.46, "end": 683.46, "text": " that the personality of Kali"}, {"start": 683.46, "end": 685.46, "text": " will flourish."}, {"start": 685.46, "end": 686.46, "text": " We discussed in detail"}, {"start": 686.46, "end": 688.46, "text": " the influence of Kali."}, {"start": 688.46, "end": 690.46, "text": " Kali's influence is"}, {"start": 690.46, "end": 694.46, "text": " to entice people"}, {"start": 694.46, "end": 696.46, "text": " to engage in irreligion,"}, {"start": 696.46, "end": 699.46, "text": " adharma bandhu."}, {"start": 699.46, "end": 701.46, "text": " So people become sinful"}, {"start": 701.46, "end": 703.46, "text": " and they miss the"}, {"start": 703.46, "end": 704.46, "text": " valuable opportunity"}, {"start": 704.46, "end": 705.46, "text": " in the human form of life"}, {"start": 705.46, "end": 707.46, "text": " to prepare oneself"}, {"start": 707.46, "end": 710.46, "text": " to go back to Godhead."}, {"start": 710.46, "end": 713.46, "text": " So Kali cannot influence people."}, {"start": 713.46, "end": 714.46, "text": " Kali cannot flourish"}, {"start": 714.46, "end": 716.46, "text": " as long as there is an emperor"}, {"start": 716.46, "end": 718.46, "text": " like Pariksit Maharaj"}, {"start": 718.46, "end": 722.46, "text": " ruling the entire world."}, {"start": 722.46, "end": 723.46, "text": " So in the purport,"}, {"start": 723.46, "end": 724.46, "text": " Srila Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 724.46, "end": 726.46, "text": " as we have already explained,"}, {"start": 726.46, "end": 727.46, "text": " the personality of Kali"}, {"start": 727.46, "end": 728.46, "text": " had entered the jurisdiction"}, {"start": 728.46, "end": 730.46, "text": " of this earth long ago"}, {"start": 730.46, "end": 731.46, "text": " and he was looking"}, {"start": 731.46, "end": 732.46, "text": " for an opportunity"}, {"start": 732.46, "end": 733.46, "text": " to spread his influence"}, {"start": 733.46, "end": 736.46, "text": " all over the world."}, {"start": 736.46, "end": 737.46, "text": " This will be explained"}, {"start": 737.46, "end": 738.46, "text": " in the next verse."}, {"start": 738.46, "end": 741.46, "text": " The very day Krishna left this planet,"}, {"start": 741.46, "end": 743.46, "text": " after winding up his pastimes"}, {"start": 743.46, "end": 745.46, "text": " at the end of Dwapar Yuga,"}, {"start": 745.46, "end": 747.46, "text": " Kali, Purusha,"}, {"start": 747.46, "end": 755.46, "text": " tried to enter the earth planet."}, {"start": 755.46, "end": 757.46, "text": " Kali was looking for an opportunity"}, {"start": 757.46, "end": 759.46, "text": " but he could not do so satisfactorily"}, {"start": 759.46, "end": 760.46, "text": " due to the presence"}, {"start": 760.46, "end": 762.46, "text": " of Maharaj Pariksit."}, {"start": 762.46, "end": 765.46, "text": " That is a way of good government."}, {"start": 765.46, "end": 766.46, "text": " The disturbing elements"}, {"start": 766.46, "end": 767.46, "text": " like the personality of Kali"}, {"start": 767.46, "end": 768.46, "text": " will always try to extend"}, {"start": 768.46, "end": 771.46, "text": " their nefarious activities."}, {"start": 771.46, "end": 772.46, "text": " But it is the duty"}, {"start": 772.46, "end": 773.46, "text": " of the able state"}, {"start": 773.46, "end": 777.46, "text": " to check them by all means."}, {"start": 777.46, "end": 780.46, "text": " Pariksit stopped Kali."}, {"start": 780.46, "end": 782.46, "text": " Of course he was ready"}, {"start": 782.46, "end": 784.46, "text": " to kill Kali Purusha."}, {"start": 784.46, "end": 786.46, "text": " But Kali Purusha surrendered."}, {"start": 786.46, "end": 789.46, "text": " Pariksit Maharaj spared his life."}, {"start": 789.46, "end": 791.46, "text": " That is the code of conduct"}, {"start": 791.46, "end": 792.46, "text": " for the king."}, {"start": 792.46, "end": 793.46, "text": " That surrendered souls"}, {"start": 793.46, "end": 796.46, "text": " should never be killed."}, {"start": 796.46, "end": 798.46, "text": " But at the same time,"}, {"start": 798.46, "end": 801.46, "text": " Kali was not given"}, {"start": 801.46, "end": 803.46, "text": " any opportunity"}, {"start": 803.46, "end": 806.46, "text": " for spreading his evil influence"}, {"start": 806.46, "end": 809.46, "text": " among the citizens"}, {"start": 809.46, "end": 812.46, "text": " of Pariksit Maharaj's kingdom."}, {"start": 812.46, "end": 814.46, "text": " Although Maharaj Pariksit"}, {"start": 814.46, "end": 815.46, "text": " allotted places"}, {"start": 815.46, "end": 817.46, "text": " for the personality of Kali,"}, {"start": 817.46, "end": 818.46, "text": " at the same time"}, {"start": 818.46, "end": 819.46, "text": " he gave no chance"}, {"start": 819.46, "end": 820.46, "text": " for the citizens"}, {"start": 820.46, "end": 822.46, "text": " which swayed by the personality of Kali."}, {"start": 822.46, "end": 824.46, "text": " How did he do that?"}, {"start": 824.46, "end": 829.46, "text": " He actually utilized"}, {"start": 829.46, "end": 833.46, "text": " all the stored gold"}, {"start": 833.46, "end": 836.46, "text": " for propagating the glories"}, {"start": 836.46, "end": 838.46, "text": " of the Supreme Lord Krishna"}, {"start": 838.46, "end": 841.46, "text": " for Krishna's Sankirtana."}, {"start": 841.46, "end": 842.46, "text": " And that is the way"}, {"start": 842.46, "end": 845.46, "text": " to prevent the influence"}, {"start": 845.46, "end": 847.46, "text": " of Kali."}, {"start": 847.46, "end": 850.46, "text": " If people"}, {"start": 850.46, "end": 853.46, "text": " do not use their"}, {"start": 853.46, "end": 855.46, "text": " excess wealth"}, {"start": 855.46, "end": 857.46, "text": " beyond what they require,"}, {"start": 857.46, "end": 858.46, "text": " minimum required"}, {"start": 858.46, "end": 859.46, "text": " for their bodily maintenance,"}, {"start": 859.46, "end": 860.46, "text": " beyond that,"}, {"start": 860.46, "end": 861.46, "text": " if they don't use"}, {"start": 861.46, "end": 862.46, "text": " the excess wealth"}, {"start": 862.46, "end": 864.46, "text": " for Sankirtana,"}, {"start": 864.46, "end": 866.46, "text": " for Krishna consciousness,"}, {"start": 866.46, "end": 868.46, "text": " then that accumulated wealth"}, {"start": 868.46, "end": 870.46, "text": " becomes the"}, {"start": 870.46, "end": 872.46, "text": " place for breeding"}, {"start": 872.46, "end": 874.46, "text": " all kinds of"}, {"start": 874.46, "end": 879.46, "text": " sinful activities."}, {"start": 879.46, "end": 880.46, "text": " Like it is happening now,"}, {"start": 880.46, "end": 882.46, "text": " we can see"}, {"start": 882.46, "end": 884.46, "text": " that people use"}, {"start": 884.46, "end": 887.46, "text": " their excess wealth"}, {"start": 887.46, "end": 889.46, "text": " simply for sinful ways"}, {"start": 889.46, "end": 894.46, "text": " of enjoying sense gratification."}, {"start": 894.46, "end": 895.46, "text": " So that chance"}, {"start": 895.46, "end": 896.46, "text": " was not given"}, {"start": 896.46, "end": 897.46, "text": " because of the"}, {"start": 897.46, "end": 899.46, "text": " strong governance"}, {"start": 899.46, "end": 900.46, "text": " of Pariksit Maharaj"}, {"start": 900.46, "end": 901.46, "text": " and that's being said here."}, {"start": 901.46, "end": 902.46, "text": " I'll stop here."}, {"start": 902.46, "end": 903.46, "text": " Thank you very much."}, {"start": 903.46, "end": 904.46, "text": " Hare Krishna."}]}